metadata.name: Loma Blanca
metadata.description:
For each 360 VR NFT collected on SuperRare the collector will be dropped a wide angle Panorama of the 360 degree image on SuperRare.

Loma Blanca is part of Ty Lekki's genesis series, Vertigo, on SuperRare. The mysterious west face of the Fitz Roy massif has rarely ever been photographed. After years of planning and multiple failed attempts, I was finally able to get the shot I was after. It took three nights to get to the summit of Loma Blanca where I was were able to capture some of the most unique photos ever taken from Patagonia. This image is viewable in VR on SuperRare. 

https://superrare.com/0x250ff17091c3c8beddc32c6ce66f2e896c07acb7/loma-blanca-1
